---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import { withLocalePath } from '../../i18n/locale';

const homeHref = withLocalePath('/', 'ru');
const odrHref = 'https://ec.europa.eu/consumers/odr';
const schlichtungHref = 'https://www.verbraucher-schlichter.de';
---

<BaseLayout
	locale="ru"
	title="Imprint"
	description="Legal information Prime Realty pursuant to DDG & MStV (Germany). Courtesy translation – German version authoritative where required by law."
>
	<div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 py-12 md:py-16">
		<article class="glass-panel px-8 py-10 md:px-10 md:py-14">
			<h1 class="font-heading-display text-3xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-gray-900 md:text-4xl">Imprint</h1>
			<p class="mt-3 text-sm text-slate-600">
				Information pursuant to Section 5 German Digital Services Act (DDG); registered office in Germany.
			</p>

			<section class="mt-12 space-y-4 text-sm leading-relaxed text-slate-700">
				<h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900">Prime Realty · Real Estate by the Sea</h2>
				<p>
					Panoramastraße 13<br />
					73765 Neuhausen, Deutschland
				</p>

				<h3 class="pt-6 text-base font-semibold text-gray-900">Contact</h3>
				<p>
					E-mail:
					<a href="mailto:info@prime-realty.de" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-muted"> info@prime-realty.de</a><br />
					Tel.: +49 (0) 711 252 55 610
				</p>

				<h3 class="pt-6 text-base font-semibold text-gray-900">VAT ID</h3>
				<p>
					Value added tax identification number pursuant to § 27 a German VAT Act (UStG):<br />
					<span class="text-gray-900">DE294960838</span>
				</p>

				<h3 class="pt-6 text-base font-semibold text-gray-900">Responsible for editorial content pursuant to § 18 (2) German Media Treaty (MStV)</h3>
				<p>
					Prime Realty<br />
					Panoramastraße 13<br />
					73765 Neuhausen, Deutschland
				</p>

				<h2 class="pt-14 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Disclaimer</h2>

				<h3 class="pt-6 text-base font-semibold text-gray-900">Content</h3>
				<p>
					As service provider within the meaning of § 7 (1) DDG we are responsible for our own content on these pages.
					Under §§ 8–10 DDG we are not obligated to monitor third-party transmitted or stored information or to search for
					circumstances indicating unlawful activity.
				</p>
				<p>
					Legal obligations to remove or block the use of information remain unaffected; liability attaches only upon
					knowledge of a specific infringement—will remove such material without delay upon notice.
				</p>
				<p>
					<strong class="font-medium text-gray-900">Digital Services Act (DSA):</strong> You may report alleged illegal content by e-mail to{' '}
					<a href="mailto:info@prime-realty.de" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-muted"> info@prime-realty.de</a>.
				</p>

				<h3 class="pt-6 text-base font-semibold text-gray-900">Links</h3>
				<p>
					Our site may contain links to external third-party sites over whose content we have no control; we cannot
					accept liability for that content. The linked pages were checked at the time of linking for obvious legal
					violations; permanent monitoring without concrete indication is not reasonable; known infringements will be
					removed promptly.
				</p>

				<h3 class="pt-6 text-base font-semibold text-gray-900">Copyright</h3>
				<p>
					Content on this site is subject to German copyright law. Reproduction, editing, distribution or any use
					outside statutory limits requires prior written consent. Downloads and copies are permitted only for private,
					non-commercial use.
				</p>

				<h2 class="pt-14 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">EU online dispute resolution</h2>
				<p>
					The European Commission provides a platform for online dispute resolution:{' '}
					<a href={odrHref} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-muted break-all">
						{odrHref}
					</a>
					<br />
					Our e-mail address is shown above.
				</p>

				<h2 class="pt-14 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Consumer arbitration</h2>
				<p>
					We are neither willing nor obliged to participate in dispute resolution before a consumer arbitration board.
				</p>

				<h3 class="pt-6 text-base font-semibold text-gray-900">VSBG notice</h3>
				<p>
					We do not participate in dispute resolution before a consumer arbitration board. Under German law we must point
					you to a competent body:
				</p>
				<p>
					<strong class="font-medium text-gray-900">General Consumer Conciliation Board of Zentrum für Schlichtung e.V.</strong><br />
					Straßburger Straße 8<br />
					77694 Kehl am Rhein<br />
					<a href={schlichtungHref} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-muted break-all">
						{schlichtungHref}
					</a>
				</p>

				<h2 class="pt-14 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">Information under Regulation (EU) 2019/1150 (P2B)</h2>
				<p>Key parameters for ranking and related points:</p>
				<ul class="mt-4 list-disc space-y-2 pl-5 text-slate-300 marker:text-accent">
					<li><span class="text-gray-900">Main ranking parameters:</span> relevance, recency, price, location</li>
					<li>
						<span class="text-gray-900">Access to personal data:</span>{' '}
						<a href="/en/datenschutz" class="text-accent hover:text-accent-muted">Privacy policy</a>
					</li>
					<li><span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Restrictions on ancillary goods/services:</span> none</li>
					<li><span class="font-medium text-gray-900">Effect of GTC changes on listings:</span> communicated in advance</li>
				</ul>

				<h2 class="pt-14 text-xl font-bold text-gray-900">AI Act (Regulation (EU) 2024/1689)</h2>
				<p>
					This website does not currently use AI systems within the meaning of the AI Act. Should AI-supported features
					(e.g. chatbots) be introduced in future, we will inform you transparently.
				</p>
			</section>

			<p class="mt-14">
				<a href={homeHref} class="text-sm font-semibold text-amber-900 hover:text-amber-950">← Back to home</a>
			</p>
		</article>
	</div>
</BaseLayout>
